OL,3,CThree people charged with Blackburn
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FThree people have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder after a man was fatally stabbed
OL,8,Fin Blackburn.
OL,10,FA Home Office Post Mortem examination
OL,11,Fconcluded Paul Scott died from a
OL,12,Fsingle knife wound.
OL,14,FPolice were called out at 3:40am on
OL,15,F22nd June, where they found the victim
OL,16,Funresponsive at an address on Peridot
OL,17,FClose.
OL,19,F37-year-old Paul was pronounced dead
OL,20,Fat the scene.
