OL,3,CThree people charged with Blackburn
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FLancashire Police say his death is
OL,7,Fbeing treated as an isolated incident,
OL,8,Fand there is no threat to the wider
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,FThree people were arrested on Sunday
OL,12,Fmorning and have now been charged.
OL,14,FLiam Donlin, 24, Joanne Maxwell, 43,
OL,15,Fand Amie Clegg, 21, all of Lynwood
OL,16,FAvenue, Darwen, have been charged with
OL,17,Fmurder and have been remanded to
OL,18,Fappear before Blackburn Magistrates
OL,19,FCourt tomorrow (25th June).
