OL,6,FDCI John McNamara, of our Force Major
OL,7,FInvestigation Team said: "First and
OL,8,Fforemost, my, and my team's thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with Paul's family and loved
OL,10,Fones at what is an incredibly
OL,11,Fdifficult time."
OL,13,F"Three people have now been charged
OL,14,Fwith murder in connection with Paul's
OL,15,Fdeath, but our investigation is very
OL,16,Fmuch ongoing."
